{"thag4.9:0.1":"Theragatha 4.9 ","thag4.9:0.2":"Catukkanipata ","thag4.9:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag4.9:0.4":"Candanattheragatha ","thag4.9:1.1":"“Jatarupena sanchanna, ","thag4.9:1.2":"dasiganapurakkhata; ","thag4.9:1.3":"Ankena puttamadaya, ","thag4.9:1.4":"bhariya mam upagami. ","thag4.9:2.1":"Tanca disvana ayantim, ","thag4.9:2.2":"sakaputtassa mataram; ","thag4.9:2.3":"Alankatam suvasanam, ","thag4.9:2.4":"maccupasamva odditam. ","thag4.9:3.1":"Tato me manasikaro, ","thag4.9:3.2":"yoniso udapajjatha; ","thag4.9:3.3":"Adinavo paturahu, ","thag4.9:3.4":"nibbida samatitthatha. ","thag4.9:4.1":"Tato cittam vimucci me, ","thag4.9:4.2":"passa dhammasudhammatam; ","thag4.9:4.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","thag4.9:4.4":"katam buddhassa sasanan”ti. ","thag4.9:4.5":"… Candano thero …. "}